            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>埃克森美孚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:XOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/XOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">XOM-US</a>)截至台北時間09日02:08股價下跌10.1美元，報153.81美元，跌幅6.16%，成交量18,822,737（股），盤中最高價155.74美元、最低價150.98美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.6%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.39%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+2.95%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+6.38%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>埃克森美孚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:XOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/XOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">XOM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-3.39%</li> <li>近 1 月：+8.4%</li> <li>近 3 月：+38.33%</li> <li>近 6 月：+43.45%</li> <li>今年以來：+36.21%</li></ul></section></main>",
